  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The land of Aria is being invaded by goblins and monsters of unknown origin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The elves constructed a summoning circle to summon an other world wanderer to save them from the monster horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HELP YOUR ELF</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with Elena the elf and take on cute monsters with powerful magical arsenal of weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988420/extras/b313d998b6e84ef070f8e8769c83d0a0.poster.avif?t=1735485804\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988420/extras/b313d998b6e84ef070f8e8769c83d0a0.webm?t=1735485804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988420/extras/b313d998b6e84ef070f8e8769c83d0a0.mp4?t=1735485804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT MONSTERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through cute monsters. Collect fantasy-based powerups and blast through your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have a blast traversing through the stylized bright beautiful arena</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT ITEMS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect scrolls to unlock new areas on the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay is classic retro arena shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use vibrant powerful weapons to defeat your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988420/extras/0f1150bec9790f91e4f1aa1b557de2f4.poster.avif?t=1735485804\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988420/extras/0f1150bec9790f91e4f1aa1b557de2f4.webm?t=1735485804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988420/extras/0f1150bec9790f91e4f1aa1b557de2f4.mp4?t=1735485804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GORGEOUS ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an Anime themed Arena Shooter game with the classic arena-style weapon system with a fantasy twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features fantasy-based weapon system.</p>",
